<div class="thumbinner" style="width:172px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Samba_Parade_-_Rio%27s_Carnival_2008.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Samba_Parade_-_Rio%27s_Carnival_2008.jpg/170px-Samba_Parade_-_Rio%27s_Carnival_2008.jpg" width="170" height="128" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Samba_Parade_-_Rio%27s_Carnival_2008.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.20wmf5/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Samba parade at Rio de Janeiro, 2008.</div>
